== Installation notes == 
Download and install [http://www.macports.org/ macports]

Install sqlite through macports with the command: "port install sqlite3". Now you should be good to compile xmms2 on your Mac OS X Tiger.

== CoreAudio output ==
XMMS2 has Native support for CoreAudio, no more fulhack as in XMMS1 using a hacked ESD.

